high_descs: Walk forward until you hit the table then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the loaf of bread by the wall.
Position yourself so you  are in front of the stove facing it.
Cook the loaf of bread in the microwave then remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the wall then turn right.
Place the bread on the table near the edge laying lengthwise along the table near the middle.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot loaf of bread on a white table.

high_descs: Turn right and head towards the bread on the counter.
Turn right, take a few steps and then turn left to face the stove.
Look up to find the microwave.
Heat up the bread in the microwave on top of the stove and take it out.
Turn around head towards the wall, and then turn right to find the table.
Place the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the bread to place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and locate the counter beside the stove.
Pick up the piece of bread.
Turn all the way around to the stove on the right.
Put the bread in the microwave and turn it on. Remove the bread when it's finished.
Turn to the left and the follow to the right to the small white table.
Put the bread down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Warm a loaf of bread and move it to a table.
